fields.name: DnsZoneResourceId
fields.description: Resource ID of the DNS Zone to be associated with the web app. Used only when Web App Routing is enabled.

fields.name: Enabled
fields.description: Whether to enable Web App Routing.

fields.name: Identity
fields.description: Managed identity of the Web Application Routing add-on. This is the identity that should be granted permissions, for example, to manage the associated Azure DNS resource and get certificates from Azure Key Vault. See [this overview of the add-on](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/aks/web-app-routing?tabs=with-osm) for more instructions.
